snippet.title: Kesha in 2011 Deposition: 'Dr. Luke Never Made Sexual Advances at Me'
snippet.description: Kesha broke her silence on Tuesday night to thank supporters following her failed bid to get out of her contract with producer Dr. Luke. The singer claims Dr. Luke raped and sexually assaulted her. He denies the allegations and has not been charged with any crime.  "The support I have received has left my face swollen from tears. I love you all so much," she wrote on Instagram. A 2011 deposition surfaced showing Kesha denying Dr. Luke, committed any acts of sexual misconduct. #InsideEdition
